            We work with state of the art
            factories in South America and Asia, specializing in the highest quality prefinished solid hardwood flooring
            available.</p> 

            <p>Our flooring partners in manufacturing use the latest technology to produce a precision milled and properly kiln
            dried hardwood flooring and decking product. We require extensive quality control at every stage of the flooring manufacturing process. The final step in
            the process is to apply an aluminum oxide factory finish. This 8 coat process applied to our elemental hardwood flooring includes sanding, sealer, aluminum oxide
            which gives the finish its hardness, and then the final top coat. Our prefinished elemental hardwood flooring carries a 25 year warranty
            for residential use.</p>

            <h3>Elemental Hardwood Exotic Flooring</h3>

            <p>We specialize in most South American Exotic species including Brazilian Cherry, Ipe or Brazilian Walnut, TigerWood,
            Cumaru, Red Cumaru or Dark Cumaru, Massaranduba or Paraju, and many other Brazilian Amazon woods.</p>

            <p>We also source material from Bolivia and Paraguay including Lapacho Ipe, Amendoim, Kurupayra or Angico, 
            Tarara or Canary Wood, Tiete Rosewood or Sirari, and Curupau or Patagonian Rosewood. Many of these flooring species have
            multiple names so please visit our prefinished elemental hardwood flooring catalog to learn more and see our many photos.</p>      
                  
